docs.title: Wuthering Waves Guide
docs.text:
The calculations provided on this website may contain various errors; please take note before referencing.

Due to a lack of peer review and occasional personal oversight, errors frequently occur in inputting and calculating. If there are any mistakes, they are definitely just errors!
